{"tid":2256794,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我表弟話佢自己係魔界二皇子...因為比唔知乜春撞到所以e家跌左落黎凡間","createTime":"2020-10-24T15:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T03:45:39.000Z","uid":248834,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"25f39a25359f8cb81ce40ed9722f58dc4814bd8b","tid":2256794,"uid":248834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n頭先夜晚去左表弟屋企食飯<br />\n因為好多年冇見了<br />\n原來佢已經小5<br />\n<br />\n一上到去，佢變得好撚奇怪<br />\n好怕生保人，因為太耐無見<br />\n成個白痴仔咁周圍閃黎閃去<br />\n閃撚完跟住縮埋係角落頭<br />\n直情係雙腳抱膝咁抱住自己<br />\n兼有一張細細地既被跟住自己方便包住自己<br />\n<br />\n好喇，係咁撩下佢，慢慢開始有計傾<br />\n但一發不可收拾，佢一直up左成個鐘<br />\n雖然內容係好天馬行空<br />\n但好工整咁講哂成個內容<br />\n大約就係話 (好多都唔記得，大約)<br />\n<br />\n自己係來自乜乜星球<br />\n係魔界二皇子，有個妹<br />\n但唔知比列車定係乜春野撞到所以跌左落黎凡間<br />\n果到有精靈 乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁 我都係聽完就算<br />\n然後最不可思議<br />\n佢之後索性wts我，整理哂佢星球既野<br />\n成段咁比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有 4張相<br />\n分好1 2 3 4 怕撈亂<br />\n內容:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪我脫節太耐<br />\n呢d內容有冇相關遊戲係近似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c526ddfcaf03e3aaa75eb4a82ed4b092b757d23e","tid":2256794,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883b52e679ac56f92473d3fee2aa29f6d9c3b9ff","tid":2256794,"uid":198900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"lm待笑"},{"pid":"4bb0098f8b2b7ce26ec3c05adf807ad9685eef39","tid":2256794,"uid":201604,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"叫佢帶我地移民得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f548d5242495f7997e2e9cf13c1661131f2656","tid":2256794,"uid":287326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"你話佢係你魔界契弟<br />\n<br />\n叫佢唔好咁揚"},{"pid":"0db6cb280b180926e7cc37cfc2263c44984cf68a","tid":2256794,"uid":325131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ac585c585d9102295aa78da9e67489ae845f3631","tid":2256794,"uid":2949,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:00.000Z","msg":"你表弟咁早熟<br />\n小五就有中二病"},{"pid":"43c17024eccf8b755d1a7fb6cd518abef5495bb1","tid":2256794,"uid":335664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"帶佢去睇精神科醫生"},{"pid":"ef9a908dc50ecfa41564e3a14b3695d5f39e57bb","tid":2256794,"uid":311835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd8db3ca4378a42994717715c698f6ce13eefea","tid":2256794,"uid":245484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"問佢有冇比朋友打開過邪王真眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be7a5cfe8724bbe5bd1437929f7a36900fd9e94","tid":2256794,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"Lucifer"},{"pid":"671fc04fe7b47e49da9da3c43995f771c8a0f434","tid":2256794,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9e7e073cdf62c279608825f5eba0d84710b6c9","tid":2256794,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"以前有個中學同學 大個咗都係咁 之後入咗青山正常返<br />\n但食精神科藥食到變咗肥佬"},{"pid":"1f1c7429618aa9db7d68a3787bafcebfc54b873a","tid":2256794,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"咁細個就咁重中二病<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" c