 />\n不過大家放過佢啦 佢仲係讀緊小五<br />\n佢老豆老母都好辛苦 要照顧佢<br />\n佢細細個已經食雞唔食雞皮 食橙食埋橙皮<br />\n我代佢係呢度向大家道歉一聲"},{"pid":"98c1c71db9ecb0076e0309d310de00e6a8e5172b","tid":2256794,"uid":204370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"玩星願小王子玩上腦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b475dc2462b86cfd1f44cc5b1611a6ba7027b917","tid":2256794,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a03a178ae97fc1399b2f3fdb495276fab90afb3","tid":2256794,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f1c7429618aa9db7d68a3787bafcebfc54b873a","tid":2256794,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"咁細個就咁重中二病<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"仲要妹控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過做乜鳩開喺學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係想學術台人士幫佢諗計醫佢個細佬"},{"pid":"bc68e9f854bf8e88f90f5adcc0c53b82dd9560ee","tid":2256794,"uid":83602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗酬期比佢返去一統魔界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3d72207b47c7f3ac108ab1aa911a1cbb56e271","tid":2256794,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"想知係邊隻game"},{"pid":"d91cf2b43cb50490a99ff04d0f90e3195093bfc1","tid":2256794,"uid":49853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/11Cz4fO4YfhMOY/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/